            <title>[HIVE-17679] http-generic-click-jacking for WebHcat server</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-17679</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The web UIs do not include the &quot;X-Frame-Options&quot; header to prevent the pages from being framed from another site.&lt;br/&gt;
Reference:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Clickjacking&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Clickjacking&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
